Hi Chris,

You're saying it starts, but won't idle. Will it keep running if you  
give it more throttle?

If not,  are you sure the fuel pump is getting power when the key is  
on and the flap in the AFM is depressed? If not, the problem is in  
the AFM switch or the double relay.

